graph TD
    Start([Start Import]) --> Source{File Source}
    Source -->|Folder Watcher| Watcher[Detect .adv / .adz in /adventures]
    Source -->|UI Upload| Upload[API: POST /api/adventures/import]
    
    Watcher --> LoadFile[Load File Content]
    Upload --> LoadFile
    
    LoadFile --> TypeCheck{File Type?}
    TypeCheck -->|.adz| Unzip[Extract ZIP Archive]
    TypeCheck -->|.adv| ParseJSON[Parse JSON Manifest]
    
    Unzip --> ExtractManifest[Read adventure.adv]
    ExtractManifest --> ParseJSON
    
    ParseJSON --> CreateTemplate[Create AdventureTemplate DB Record]
    CreateTemplate --> Assets[Move Images to /data/adventures/{id}/]
    Assets --> CreateAvatar[Create Avatar & Sync Protagonist Stats]
    CreateAvatar --> CreateSession[Create GameSession<br/>(Denormalize Title & Image)]
    CreateSession --> CreateState[Create SessionState<br/>(Set Starting Scene & Items)]
    
    CreateState --> Cleanup[Delete Source File (if Folder Watcher)]
    Cleanup --> End([Import Complete])
